title: Week 2 Recap 2022
description:
Field Yates and Daniel Dopp recap everything you need to know from Week 2 of the NFL season including the significance of the key stud and dud performances from Sunday. Plus, Liz Loza joins to recap Sunday Night Football surrounding a big night from the Packers’ backfield.
